"v.与…一致；提供食宿 【考】 obliterate : remove / accommodate : supply(同义: 删除=去除/供应=供给 ) 【记】 ac+commod(方便)+ate →给人方便→提供食 宿); 【同】 派生词: accommodation(n. 住宿)同根词: commodity(商品), commodious(宽敞的) v. 提供, 供应; 提供食宿 = bestow = domicile; 容纳; 使...适应; 与...一致 = conform 【例】accommodate (sb)for the night 留(某人)住一夜The guests are well accommodated 待客周到. accommodate (sb) with 向(某人)供应[提供] 【记】commod适合的－使人合适－提供食宿－供应 【参】commodious(adj 宽敞的); accommodation(n 住宿)commodity(n 商品) 【类】obliterate: remove = accommodate: supply删除 = 去除 = 供应 = 供给 【记】ac + commodity 有用的日用品，向别人提供用品的，对别人有用，有帮助的；com + modern现代是商品社会，供给商品来招待 accommodate (v.)  1530s, from Latin accomodatus ""suitable,"" past participle of accomodare ""make fit, adapt, fit one thing to another,"" from ad- ""to"" (see ad-) + commodare ""make fit,"" from commodus ""fit"" (see commode). Related: Accommodated; accommodating."
